<h4>
    Kinematic Equation Requirements
</h4>

<ul class = 'definition'>
    <li>
        The Kinematic Equations are valid whenever something is moving with a constant acceleration.
    </li>
    <li>
        Whenever acceleration is changing, the kinematic equations are not valid.
        You would instead need to use differential and integral calculus.
    </li>
</ul>